{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be professional and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>EcoChic Fashion</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #c0392b;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid #e74c3c;\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 15px;\n            background-color: #e74c3c;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        nav a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: #f4f4f4;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 30px auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #c0392b;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .hero h2 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 2em;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .about, .products, .contact {\n            background-color: white;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        .about h3, .products h3, .contact h3 {\n            color: #c0392b;\n            border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n        .product-item {\n            border: 1px solid #e74c3c;\n            padding: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .product-item h4 {\n            margin: 10px 0 5px 0;\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            color: #c0392b;\n        }\n        .product-item p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n        .product-item .price {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #c0392b;\n        }\n        .contact form {\n            display: grid;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n        .contact input, .contact textarea {\n            width: 100%;\n            padding: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #e74c3c;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            box-sizing: border-box; /* Include padding and border in the element's total width and height */\n        }\n        .contact button {\n            background-color: #c0392b;\n            color: white;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #e74c3c;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #333;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n        }\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>EcoChic Fashion</h1>\n    </header>\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n        <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <h2>Style with a Conscience</h2>\n        <p>Discover our collection of beautifully crafted, sustainable fashion made from eco-friendly materials. Look good, feel good, do good.</p>\n    </section>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n            <h3>Our Commitment to Sustainability</h3>\n            <p>At EcoChic Fashion, we believe that fashion and environmental responsibility can go hand in hand. We source only the finest organic and recycled materials, employ ethical manufacturing practices, and strive to minimize our carbon footprint at every step. Our mission is to provide you with stylish, high-quality clothing that you can wear with pride, knowing it's made with respect for the planet and its people.</p>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"products\" class=\"products\">\n            <h3>Our Collections</h3>\n            <div class=\"product-grid\">\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Organic+Tee\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-Shirt\">\n                    <h4>Organic Cotton Tee</h4>\n                    <p>Soft, breathable, and made from 100% GOTS-certified organic cotton.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$45.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Recycled+Denim\" alt=\"Recycled Denim Jeans\">\n                    <h4>Recycled Denim Jeans</h4>\n                    <p>Classic fit jeans crafted from post-consumer recycled denim.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$95.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/c0392b/ffffff?text=Linen+Dress\" alt=\"Linen Midi Dress\">\n                    <h4>Linen Midi Dress</h4>\n                    <p>Lightweight and airy midi dress, perfect for warm days, made from European flax linen.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$120.00</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/e74c3c/ffffff?text=Hemp+Sweater\" alt=\"Hemp Blend Sweater\">\n                    <h4>Hemp Blend Sweater</h4>\n                    <p>A cozy and durable sweater made from a blend of hemp and organic cotton.</p>\n                    <p class=\"price\">$85.00</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\">\n            <h3>Get in Touch</h3>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 EcoChic Fashion. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}